{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-007__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-007", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·007.1", "text_original": "明明上天，照臨下土。我征徂西，至于艽野。二月初吉，載離寒暑。\n心之憂矣，其毒大苦。念彼共人，涕零如雨。豈不懷歸？畏此罪罟。", "text_normalized": "明明上天，照臨下土。我征徂西，至于艽野。二月初吉，載離寒暑。\n心之憂矣，其毒大苦。念彼共人，涕零如雨。豈不懷歸？畏此罪罟。", "notes": "小明 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-007__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-007", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·007.2", "text_original": "嗟爾君子，無恆安處。靖共爾位，正直是與。神之聽之，式穀以女。", "text_normalized": "嗟爾君子，無恆安處。靖共爾位，正直是與。神之聽之，式穀以女。", "notes": "小明 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-007__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-007", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·007.3", "text_original": "嗟爾君子，無恆安息。靖共爾位，好是正直。神之聽之，介爾景福。", "text_normalized": "嗟爾君子，無恆安息。靖共爾位，好是正直。神之聽之，介爾景福。", "notes": "小明 Chinese stanza 3."}
